  "texts": [
    "AI assessmentsAn equally difficult question is how such AI models can be tested for their ethical and legal compliance, and to which standards they should conform.",
    "AI can be tested using a combination of technical standards, regulatory requirements, and ethical considerations.",
    "Technical standards play a key role in mitigating the risks associated with AI by defining technical requirements for the development and testing of AI systems [15].",
    "These standards can cover aspects such as safety, non-discrimination, and reliability.",
    "Regulatory requirements, such as those outlined by the FDA, involve testing medical products using computer models, simulations, and virtual trials enhanced by artificial intelligence to ensure safety and efficacy [83]."
  ]
}